== Overview ==

Offering more deflection power than the standard [[Baron Shield]], the Baron Reflective will sustain more damage but will require longer recharge times.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron Reflective Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
